MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

91-2386. State ex rel. Scheiman v. Warrensville Hts.

In Mandamus. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of mandamus. Upon consideration of the joint application to dismiss with prejudice,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that said application be, and the same is hereby, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
